cs351.utility

Class Vector2f

  • java.lang.Object
    • cs351.utility.Vector2f

  • public class Vector2f
extends java.lang.Object
    Vector2f can maintain double values for x/y components and perform some vector operations with them.

    • Constructor Summary

      Copy constructor - creates a new Vector2f with the values of the given Vector2f.
